data.description: Location, location, location!  This spacious townhome is located in highly desirable Plymouth just minutes from shopping, dining and freeway access.  Featuring an open floor plan with bamboo floors throughout main living spaces, spacious bedrooms, gas burning fireplace, sky light for added natural light and a private deck off the living room.  Attached garage and plenty of guest parking. NEW AC, Furnace & Water Heater within the last 4 years.  A short distance from the property you will find beautiful paths leading to Nature Canyon Park.
